data.description: Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with a one-car garage in the heart of West Wichita. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this property offers comfort, convenience, and a warm, welcoming atmosphere that's perfect for families and those seeking a cozy place to call home. Key Features: 3 spacious bedrooms provide ample room for your family or guests, each boasting plenty of natural light and closet space.The well-appointed bathroom offers functionality and style, featuring modern fixtures and a bathtub/shower combination.The one-car garage provides secure parking and extra storage space for your convenience. This home also features a large back yard that can be turned into your own private oasis! This home won't last long, so schedule your showing today!
